snippet.title: Johnny Rocketfingers (Flash Game) [No Commentary]
snippet.description: I'm not into stickman games, inlcuding this one. I don't even want to make a gameplay for it, way too many copyrighted soundtracks for a stickman game. I do it just because a dude request me to, don't ask me why he wants me to play this.
